topic.title: Postprocedure Diagnosis - conformance rules

section.p: The Postprocedure Diagnosis entry encodes the diagnosis or diagnoses discovered or confirmed during the procedure. Often it is the same as the pre-procedure diagnosis or indication.

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:16766, CONF:16767 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.51"
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ACT" Act (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass) (CONF:8756, R2.1=CONF:1198-8756)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood) (CONF:8757, R2.1=CONF:1198-8757)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code/@code="59769-0" Postprocedure Diagnosis (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:8758)

SHALL contain [1..*] entryRelationship such that it (CONF:8759, CONF:8760, CONF:15583)
Contains @typeCode="SUBJ" SUBJ
Conforms to Problem Observation[Observation: templateId 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.4] (templateId: 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.4)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ACT" Act (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass) (CONF:8756, R2.1=CONF:1198-8756)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood) (CONF:8757, R2.1=CONF:1198-8757)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code/@code="59769-0" Postprocedure Diagnosis (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:8758)

SHALL contain [1..*] entryRelationship such that it (CONF:8759, CONF:8760, CONF:15583)
Contains @typeCode="SUBJ" SUBJ
Conforms to Problem Observation[Observation: templateId 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.4] (templateId: 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.4)
